## Guidelines

- Focus on meaningful issues, not nits
- If nothing qualifies, report `No significant issues found`
- Keep the report short and concrete
- Do not write `PASS` or emit `REVIEW_PASSED` unless the report includes the exact commands run and all required local verification is green

